| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4972 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0f39f454-6a82-5c2d-8aeb-3ace99a36c20"
